ComicInfo.Summary: Lady Death returns to the Under Realm from her self-imposed exile in the nightmarish dimension of The Void... But nothing, including Hope herself, is as it once was! Now transformed into the true personification of her namesake, Lady Death must wrestle with her new life's mission and the unbreakable deal with Death itself. Available with a Regular cover by Renato Camilo, Sultry Cover by Matt Martin, Wraparound by Michael Dipascale, and a retailer order incentive Art Deco cover by painter Dipascale!
